Dear Hiring Team, 

It is with great pleasure that I submit my candidacy for the DevOps Engineer - Infrastructure position with Kodiak Robotics. I bring over three years of professional experience in infrastructure automation, cloud systems, and end user support, along with a strong academic foundation as a Master of Science in Computer Science graduate from Pace University, NY.

